{"name":"Opportunities","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","description":"Deepnight Revelation, Book 3, pg. 29","results":[{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"UXr96W3ZS056gRqT","text":"The Travellers gain knowledge of something very special in the local region. This might be a previously unknown civilisation, wondrous phenomenon or source of rare materials.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"EQ7WEdAN4ENbZ1BZ","text":"During the task the Travellers make a valuable find, such as a stash of components mislabelled and forgotten in an obscure storeroom.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"aDWdbYkbLzvRuHT3","text":"Some of the crew have found a way to fix a previously impossible problem. The Travellers gain a free repair effort (see Repairs and Replacements on page 58) or similar advantage.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"AymLkVenFVY2LRm2","text":"A piece of highly useful data is obtained. The Travellers may ‘cash in’ this find at a later date, in return for information from the Referee or a bonus to resolve tasks during a Mission.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"ywjSRiW90Tv4xAtr","text":"Routine intelligence-collation produces a lead on something worthy of investigation, such as a planetoid belt with rich resources or a star with unusual characteristics.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"fTxDvIcV8BhJM2kH","text":"The current task turns out to be much easier than expected and is completed in record time or without difficulties.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"7OnaQzgpuNALSfgT","text":"Inaccuracies in the supply logs turn out to be in favour of the Travellers for once. There are more of what is needed than expected, allowing the current task to be completed without expending resources or supplies expended this week to be effectively replaced.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[9,9],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"HkS0mB7yeyN7ogbP","text":"Someone finds additional uses for standard equipment or a technique that improves efficiency. DM+1 applies to all checks for the remainder of this Mission.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[10,10],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"djLKyZyiuNutj4ig","text":"An exceptionally good idea is presented to the Travellers, greatly simplifying current tasks. DM+1 applies to all checks to resolve tasks throughout the current Reach.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[11,11],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"548F34koTQOxq7Pl","text":"A piece of equipment aboard the Travellers’ ship turns out to be a non-standard variant with additional functions. These were not a great success and not integrated into future designs, which means few people know about them. On one occasion when the Travellers face a technical problem (for example, inability to resolve critical sensor data) this capability provides a solution.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[12,12],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"5uW7foE3wol2gfCK","text":"A non-Traveller crewmember turns out to have had a very respectable academic career or interest in an obscure subject that has now become useful. Their long-disused knowledge of obscure alien art, dead languages or rare jumpspace phenomena can be defined at any time the Travellers want, providing a solution to an otherwise difficult situation.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}}],"formula":"2D6","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"yeZEZ0XOw4URiaL8":3},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"twodsix","systemVersion":"2.32.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1694645685650,"modifiedTime":1694645801626,"lastModifiedBy":"yeZEZ0XOw4URiaL8"},"_id":"mDmzDzvSmQsoCcD7"}
